      "id": "PopularPost336042",
      "post_content": "Perhaps red is the red-haired step-child of the colors of magic. lol  \n  \nOn a serious note, I think the main injustice to mono-red in this set is that they used the 2006 slot to choose a red card, which was a multicolor-heavy expansion. They're only other reasonable options were [Demonfire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=189229) and [Rakdos Pit-Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=189230) (maybe).  \n  \n  \n... so why wasn't [Wheel of Fortune](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=202558) in FTV:Exiled?  \n  \nI think all colors got reasonable treatment in FTV: Legends.  \n  \nThe red card in FTV:Relics is [AEther Vial](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=212630) lol.",
      "posted_by": "Enchantment_Removal",
