    {
      "id": "PopularPost336168",
      "post_content": "Ravnica is my favourite plane. Always has been. In fact, I began Magic when the City of Guilds was still standard, though I didn't know about formats at the time. That block had so many good cards in it, and so I was disheartened when I saw this as its one card to represent that year, especially coming out of RTR, which, in my opinion, did not do the plane justice at all. R&D doesn't seem to like Ravnica much, at least it appears that way as of recent events. :/  \n  \nHowever I do feel somewhat vindicated to see that this card is the lowest rated card in FTV:20 since it means that at least some of you feel similar to how I do; that this was the wrong choice of card for the Ravnica block.",
      "posted_by": "MithosFall",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost336168\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Ravnica is my favourite plane.  Always has been.  In fact, I began Magic when the City of Guilds was still standard, though I didn't know about formats at the time.  That block had so many good cards in it, and so I was disheartened when I saw this as its one card to represent that year, especially coming out of RTR, which, in my opinion, did not do the plane justice at all.  R&amp;D doesn't seem to like Ravnica much, at least it appears that way as of recent events.  :/<br/><br/>However I do feel somewhat vindicated to see that this card is the lowest rated card in FTV:20 since it means that at least some of you feel similar to how I do; that this was the wrong choice of card for the Ravnica block.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy8603\">MithosFall</span>\r\n                                (8/23/2013 1:18:14 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubC